{"view":"article","slug":"blogs-mixup-3x3-2","category":"Blogs","subcategory":"Yujian Song","topDir":"Blogs","title":{"en":"三阶混元魔方"},"content":{"en":"<p><strong>三阶混元魔方</strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/blogs-mixup-3x3-2/en/image1.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>Yujian Song (宋雨键)</p><p><strong>混元类的魔方</strong></p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/blogs-mixup-3x3-2/en/image2.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/blogs-mixup-3x3-2/en/image3.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>三阶混元, Mixup 3x3x3, 图源TwistyPuzzles</p><p>三阶混元是一个很经典的魔方, 它的外观看上去和普通的三阶魔方很像, 但当中层转动45°时, 魔方仍能继续旋转, 也就是说, 这个魔方的 ”中心块” 和 ”棱块” 仅仅是外观不同, 实际上没有区别. </p><p>混元类的魔方也在异形魔方繁多的种类中占有一席之地, 从经典的三阶混元出发, 可以衍生出许许多多的混元魔方. 例如, 三阶混元的中心块宽度与棱块宽度相等, 如果改变二者, 就得到了混元魔方加强版和子母333: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/blogs-mixup-3x3-2/en/image4.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/blogs-mixup-3x3-2/en/image5.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/blogs-mixup-3x3-2/en/image6.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>Mixup 3x3x3 plus, 中心块&lt;棱块</p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/blogs-mixup-3x3-2/en/image7.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/blogs-mixup-3x3-2/en/image8.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/blogs-mixup-3x3-2/en/image9.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>子母333, 中心块&gt;棱块</p><p>也有阶数更高切割更复杂的混元: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/blogs-mixup-3x3-2/en/image10.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/blogs-mixup-3x3-2/en/image11.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/blogs-mixup-3x3-2/en/image12.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/blogs-mixup-3x3-2/en/image13.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>一些混元魔方, 图源TwistyPuzzles及阿里巴巴</p><p>三阶混元毫无疑问是复原这些魔方的基础. </p><p><strong>转动规定</strong></p><p>三阶魔方中常用<strong>E</strong>,<strong>M</strong>,<strong>S</strong>表示中层的转动, 这里将沿用该记法, 并且为了不与三阶魔方混淆, 我们在字母后加<strong>/2</strong>表示45°转动, 加<strong>/2'</strong>表示反方向45°转动. <strong>E</strong>,<strong>M</strong>,<strong>S</strong>的方向如下图: </p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/blogs-mixup-3x3-2/en/image14.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/blogs-mixup-3x3-2/en/image15.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/blogs-mixup-3x3-2/en/image16.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>E</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>M</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>S</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>其他有关面的转动规定与三阶魔方一致. </p><p><strong>第一步: 复形</strong></p><p>一种复原混元魔方的方法是先复形为正方体, 再利用三阶魔方的公式复原, 这种方法在复原子母333时也有应用. </p><p>复形可以逐层进行, 先复形底层棱块, 例如: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/blogs-mixup-3x3-2/en/image17.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"M/2' E' M/2\">M/2' E' M/2</span></p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/blogs-mixup-3x3-2/en/image18.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p><strong>F2</strong></p><p>复形中层同样可以一块一块进行置换: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/blogs-mixup-3x3-2/en/image19.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"M/2' U M/2\">M/2' U M/2</span></p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/blogs-mixup-3x3-2/en/image20.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"E/2' M/2' U M/2 E/2\">E/2' M/2' U M/2 E/2</span></p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/blogs-mixup-3x3-2/en/image21.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"M/2' U2 M/2\">M/2' U2 M/2</span></p><p>不难复形前两层, 这里不再举例. </p><p>复形顶层时, 先将中心块移至顶面中心: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/blogs-mixup-3x3-2/en/image22.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>该情形可分解为如下两个对换: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/blogs-mixup-3x3-2/en/image23.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>即有公式: <strong>S/2 R2 S/2' M/2' S/2 R2 S/2' M/2</strong></p><p>最后, 遇到错位棱块将其转化到中心块位置, 再翻转: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/blogs-mixup-3x3-2/en/image24.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img alt=\"C:\\Users\\song\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\SNAGHTML16db391.PNG\" src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/blogs-mixup-3x3-2/en/image25.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/blogs-mixup-3x3-2/en/image26.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>set up: <strong>M/2 U D'</strong></p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/blogs-mixup-3x3-2/en/image26.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img alt=\"C:\\Users\\song\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\SNAGHTML16db391.PNG\" src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/blogs-mixup-3x3-2/en/image25.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/blogs-mixup-3x3-2/en/image27.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p><strong>F</strong></p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/blogs-mixup-3x3-2/en/image27.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img alt=\"C:\\Users\\song\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\SNAGHTML16db391.PNG\" src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/blogs-mixup-3x3-2/en/image25.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/blogs-mixup-3x3-2/en/image28.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>reverse: <strong>D U' M/2'</strong></p><p>这样可以完成复形. </p><p><strong>第二步: 复原中心块</strong></p><p>类似于四阶魔方需要注意中心块的坐标, 我们在解三阶混元时, 也需要调整中心块的位置: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/blogs-mixup-3x3-2/en/image29.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"M/2' U2 M/2\">M/2' U2 M/2</span></p><p><strong>第三步: 按照三阶魔方复原并处理特殊情况</strong></p><p>复原至顶层时, 可能会遇到 ”O特” 和 “P特” , 需要用另外的方法处理. </p><p>很容易知道产生O特的原因: 因为混元魔方的中心块与棱块等价, 做一次<strong>M/2'</strong>后, 即可看作是一个中心块原地翻转180°, 利用翻转中心块的公式<strong>(R U R' U)5</strong>, 得到: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/blogs-mixup-3x3-2/en/image30.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"M/2' (R U R' U)5 M/2\">M/2' (R U R' U)5 M/2</span></p><p>通过对置换奇偶性的分析(参考 ”置换与魔方” ), 可知需要做奇置换才能复原P特, 例如做中层转动<strong>E/2</strong>, 然后再将中层块逐个归位: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/blogs-mixup-3x3-2/en/image31.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>即反复用<strong>M/2' U2 M/2</strong>将中层块与顶层中心块对换, 做<strong>(M/2' U2 M/2 E/2)8 M/2' U2 M/2</strong>. 会发现经过以上操作后出现了O特, 于是再做<strong>M/2' (R U R' U)5 M/2</strong>以及AUF: <strong>U2</strong>,<strong> </strong>即可复原. </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/blogs-mixup-3x3-2/en/image32.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"(E/2 M/2' U2 M/2)9 M/2' (R U R' U)5 M/2 U2\">(E/2 M/2' U2 M/2)9 M/2' (R U R' U)5 M/2 U2</span></p><p>至此魔方复原. </p><p><strong>另一种思路: </strong></p><p>上面我们通过转化为三阶魔方, 复原了三阶混元. 但是, 如果直接将棱块中心块视为等同, 用三循环复原所有棱块和中心块也是可以的, 在复原一些更复杂的混元魔方时常会用到三循环, 下面是几个简单的三循环公式: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/blogs-mixup-3x3-2/en/image33.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p><strong>[R', [M/2', E/2']] = R' M/2' E/2' M/2 E/2 R E/2' M/2' E/2 M/2</strong></p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/blogs-mixup-3x3-2/en/image34.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p><strong>[E/2', M/2' U2 M/2]= E/2' M/2' U2 M/2 E/2 M/2' U2 M/2</strong></p><p>另外用三阶相邻两中心块翻90°的公式, 可以得到: </p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/blogs-mixup-3x3-2/en/image35.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"S/2 R L' F B' U D' R' D U' B F' L R' U S/2'\">S/2 R L' F B' U D' R' D U' B F' L R' U S/2'</span></p>"},"algs":["M/2' E' M/2","M/2' U M/2","E/2' M/2' U M/2 E/2","M/2' U2 M/2","M/2' (R U R' U)5 M/2","(E/2 M/2' U2 M/2)9 M/2' (R U R' U)5 M/2 U2","S/2 R L' F B' U D' R' D U' B F' L R' U S/2'"],"thumb":"/stats/tutorial/media/blogs-mixup-3x3-2/en/image1.png","warningCount":0,"hasImages":true,"hasTables":true}
